dataset_description.json.Name: MB-EPI-comparison
dataset_description.json.Acknowledgements: We thank the Spinoza Centre's scanning assistants for executing the study.
dataset_description.json.HowToAcknowledge: Please cite this dataset using the corresponding DOI

onset.Description: Onset of the trial, i.e., the first display of oriented bars.

trial_type.Description: Whether the display was passive (no display), active which changed, or didn't change

Levels.passive: no display with oriented bars, only a grey screen
Levels.active_change: display with oriented bars, which changed relative to the first display
Levels.active_nochange: display with oriented bars, which DIDN'T change relative to the first display

response_accuracy.Description: Whether the response was correct, incorrect, or a miss

response_hand.Description: Which hand was used to respond
